      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S172">Mr. Harkin</sponsor>introduced
			 the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the<committee-name committee-id="SSCM00">Committee on Commerce, Science, and
			 Transportation</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
